### ===========================================
### REPORTING
### ===========================================

### 1. Seed templates from disk into MongoDB
POST {{host}}/api/reports/templates/seed
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Preview report — C51 Start List (Swimming Women, Heat 1)
### RSC format: [DIS][G][Event 18chars][Phase 4chars][Unit 6chars][SubUnit 2chars] = 34 chars
### SWMW200MFL----------HEAT0001----
POST {{host}}/api/reports/preview
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rsc": "SWMW200MFL----------HEAT0001----",
  "orisCode": "C51"
}

###

### 3. Preview report — C51 Start List (Athletics Men)
POST {{host}}/api/reports/preview
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rsc": "ATLM100M------------HEAT0001----",
  "orisCode": "C51"
}
